pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span class=\"red\">多你一個好多，少你一個唔掂！你既決定將會成為世界走向正義定係腐敗既關鍵因素！</span>"},{"pid":"59fdf894910dc8532feeabb41f9c29059ad190c0","tid":2388753,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T15:18:39.000Z","msg":"呢個先係正解"},{"pid":"d2a4e516edb0d2932e13e35ced23bc1c9c4280d7","tid":2388753,"uid":39990,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ac5ce6fad24aedc2d5b6f7ef5ce78093a990fc78","tid":2388753,"uid":228955,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T11:24:42.000Z","msg":"絕對係外國至少人哋都會尊重你哋嘅文化大陸只有打壓"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T15:21:10.000Z","msg":"外國俾人歧視同冇俾支共打壓咁難頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b75c3f44bc8291439f6ae379839080025b180751","tid":2388753,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T15:34:49.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>許冠傑</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n再會！香港！<br />\n<br />\n作詞：許冠傑/黎彼得<br />\n作曲：許冠傑<br />\n<br />\n清晨 孤身去他方<br />\n黯然 含淚滿腔<br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">立心 將理想達成<br />\n到彼邦 尋美夢 滿懷熱望</span><br />\n<br />\n親朋 祝福我安康<br />\n淒然 無話再講<br />\n立心 開拓新未來<br />\n到彼邦 圓志願 再會香港<br />\n<br />\n*用勇氣 我不怕風浪<br />\n用幹勁 縱使艱辛也闖<br />\n用鬥志 憑著熱血信心<br />\n但求達到願望 放眼望遠方<br />\n<br />\n驕陽 天邊吐金光<br />\n恍然 離淚已乾<br />\n靜觀 天際白雲<br />\n蓋高山 難眺望 再會香港*<br />\n<br />\nRepeat*<br />\n<br />\n再會香港<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=knj0sluCIro\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dknj0sluCIro&d=%2FNwPZCYHbisYOb37lcvQWosqpp%2BZ5aV1zu33iQ7YiKA%3D&h=ebcc800c\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=knj0sluCIro</a>"},{"pid":"32cc8d301f510e25b9992bb6123101a97f8ed130","tid":2388753,"uid":81113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-31T15:35:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"aa29cc460b7a1a4f5df9d035345b4f5e021b4508","tid":2388753,"uid":228955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d2a4e516edb